        "mainbody": "Commander '''Balacer Macefist''' was a [[human]] officer in charge of the [[Golden Fortress]] Military Academy in [[Eshpurta]], [[Amn]], ''circa'' the {{YearlinkName|1367}}.",
        "Activities": "Balacer Macefist oversaw the The Golden Fortress, the primary garrison and training facility of the [[Council Army]] in eastern Amn, with a total of 25,000 troops, officers, instructors, and trainees. Commander Macefist took orders from General [[Labak Craumerdaun]] but could act independently to aid the nearby city of Eshpurta if needed."
